If you haven't already got it then the first recommendation is to install ComfyUI manager as this will assist if finding most missing node packs.
https://github.com/ltdrdata/ComfyUI-Manager

IMPORTANT: first thing to check is that any model/checkpoint nodes point to a valid file on your system. This is generally the cause of most issues.

Base steps determines where Sampler 1 ends and Sample 2 starts so for a total steps of 25 Sampler 1 will end at 20 and Sampler 2 start at 20 for 5 steps. To Use only Model#1 set too 100%
